1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Totally TV is so excited to introduce our brand new kids game show, That's The Word, hosted by Jenn Barlow. That's The Word is a game show for kids, by kids. That's right, joining us are four enthusiastic kid contestants: Trinity, Lily, Lev, and Tyler.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Totally TV is so excited to introduce our brand new kids game show, That's The Word, hosted by Jenn Barlow. Kid contestants: Lily, Paris, Jonathon, and Jeff, will compete in a series of three rounds; "Secret Word", "Finish the Phrase", and "Word Scramble"
